node.text:
Do you remember all those little diecast West Coast Choppers bikes I used to sell at Wal*Mart?? 
Well my partner in that business, “Fred”. Is my partner in our Ammo business : Ammo Inc. 
Exciting times for this venture!
Not only did we just purchase Gunbroker.com. We also own Jagemann Brass in Manitowoc Wisconsin. That’s right down the road from out New Ammo Inc Facilities. I don’t usually toot my horn much on business stuff, but this one is pretty Damn cool! 

If you dig this stuff please follow these...
@ammoincusa 
@jessejamesammo 
@gunbroker 

Also if you’re interested in stock.
We are “POWW” on Nasdaq👍🏽

Thank you!🙏🏻🙏🏻

#jessejames
